âœ” Sender should close
âŒ Receiver should NOT close

1ï¸âƒ£1ï¸âƒ£ Receiving from Closed Channel
v, ok := <-ch
ok == false â†’ channel closed
v â†’ zero value

1ï¸âƒ£2ï¸âƒ£ Range Over Channel
for v := range ch {
    fmt.Println(v)
}
âœ” Stops when channel is closed.

1ï¸âƒ£3ï¸âƒ£ Sending on Closed Channel (PANIC)
