ch <- 10 // âŒ panic

1ï¸âƒ£4ï¸âƒ£ Nil Channel Behavior (TRICKY)

var ch chan int

Send blocks forever
Receive blocks forever
Used in select patterns

1ï¸âƒ£5ï¸âƒ£ Directional Channels (INTERVIEW)
func send(ch chan<- int) {}
func receive(ch <-chan int) {}
âœ” Improves safety
âœ” Documents intent

1ï¸âƒ£6ï¸âƒ£ Select Statement (PREVIEW)
